snippet.title: The Gladhollow Nasties - Early Alpha Trailer
snippet.description:
In a land where fairy tales are real, not everyone has a happy ending. When everything you do draws the monsters from make-believe one step closer to you, will you be the last one to survive?

[[We wanted to share with you an early version of how our game is coming and we look forward to showing more things we are working on in the near future. Thanks for watching!]]
